						               													<description>A compilation edition of two card games - Wizard and HeartSwitch.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This exciting new combo pack combines two of your favorite trick-taking card games into one convenient gift pack. The set includes two complete decks and instructions for two different card games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the award-winning Wizard Card Game, players try to win the exact number of tricks they bid.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Wizard deck is similar to a regular deck of playing cards with the addition of four Wizards and four Jesters. Jesters always lose and Wizards always win. When you make your exact bid, you earn points. If you take too many or too few tricks, you lose points. The special, custom Wizard Score Sheet helps players keep track of bids and points. Wizard Card Game can be played with 2-6 players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HeartSwitch is a completely new card game inspired by &amp;ldquo;Hearts&amp;rdquo;. The addition of special cards and unique concepts creates challenging situations that require Innovative strategies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The object of the game is to have the lowest score at the end of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The 60-card includes 2 good Witches and 2 bad Witches&amp;mdash;they can help you or destroy you.  Just when you are about to throw in the cards, the 4 Magicians come to your rescue!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HeartSwitch Wizard Combo Includes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HeartSwitch Card Game&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Deck of 60 Cards&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Instructions&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Custom Score Sheets&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Wizard Card Game&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Deck of 60 Cards&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Instructions&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Custom Score Sheets&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher's website&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
